text: Indira Vizcaíno Silva (born 14 January 1987) is a Mexican politician. She is a member of the Morena party. From 2009 to 2012 she was Deputy, representing Colima. In 2021, she became the second female Governor of Colima. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:People from Colima Category:Mexican politicians
